information: At Hanse Honig, we offer a selection of top-quality honey from our in-house apiary in Travemünde, a borough of Lübeck in northern Germany, as well as from our partner apiaries in the Baltic Sea area. This means that you can find premium honey which otherwise can only be bought in the relevant northern countries. We believe that it is important to act in harmony with nature and provide you with locally sourced natural products. This is why we pay particular attention to a high and sustainable quality standard. This applies both to our in-house apiary and to our partner apiaries, which we visit in person and select ourselves. We offer beekeepers a range of supplies for beekeeping and producing the perfect honey. In addition, we can provide customised honey jars which can be printed in the relevant language, thereby giving you a product that is tailor-made to your region.
